data.name: AuthTokenLoginFailed
data.value: AuthToken login failed. See ErrorCode for more details.
data.comment: Used by AuthToken when login fails.

data.name: ClientEmailIsMissingInJsonFile
data.value: Required key 'client_email' is missing in JSON secrets file.
data.comment: Used by AppConfigBase class when trying to load various settings from the JSON secrets file when using OAuth2 service account flow. Thrown if client_email key is missing in the JSON file.

data.name: ConfigSettingParseError
data.value: Failed to parse value for setting name '{0}'. Value provided: '{1}'.
data.comment: Used when a ConfigSetting cannot parse a value.

data.name: EmailCannotBeNull
data.value: Email cannot be null
data.comment: Used by AuthTokenCache when an empty email is passed to it.

data.name: FailedToLoadJsonSecretsFile
data.value: Failed to load JSON secrets file for service account configuration. See inner exception for details.
data.comment: Used by AppConfigBase class when trying to load various settings from the JSON secrets file when using OAuth2 service account flow.

data.name: FailedToParseAuthTokenException
data.value: Failed to parse response from server. See inner exception for more details.
data.comment: Used as default error message when auth token error parsing fails.

data.name: InvalidStageForSoapMessage
data.value: Invalid stage for Soap message.
data.comment: Used for ArgumentException by TraceExtension.ProcessMessage if message parameter has an invalid value for Stage field.

data.name: MalformedSoap
data.value: Failed to parse SOAP Document. Underlying error: {0}
data.comment: Used for errors parsing SOAP Documents.

data.name: MissingFactoryType
data.value: Could not locate factoryType field in Type {0}
data.comment: Used for ArgumentException when AdsUser.RegisterServices cannot locate factoryType in a registered Service.

data.name: OAuth2AuthorizationCodeIsEmpty
data.value: OAuth2 authorizationCode cannot be empty when fetching access token.
data.comment: Used to validate authorizationCode in OAuth2 flow.

data.name: OAuth2IsNotInOfflineMode
data.value: OAuth2 Offline mode should be true to refresh access token.
data.comment: Used to check if OAuth2 offline mode is enabled when refreshing access tokens.

data.name: OAuth2JwtCertificateInvalid
data.value: Unable to load private key from specified JWT certificate.
data.comment: Used by OAuth2ProviderBase if a private key cannot be loaded from OAuth2JwtCertificatePath.

data.name: OAuth2ParameterErrorMessage
data.value: Looks like your application is not configured to use OAuth2 properly. Required OAuth2 parameter {0} is missing. You may run Common\\Utils\\OAuth2TokenGenerator.cs to generate a default OAuth2 configuration.
data.comment: Thrown when a required OAuth2 parameter is missing.

data.name: PasswordCannotBeNull
data.value: Password cannot be null
data.comment: Used by AuthTokenCache when an empty password is passed to it.

data.name: PrivateKeyIsMissingInJsonFile
data.value: Required key 'private_key' is missing in JSON secrets file.
data.comment: Used by AppConfigBase class when trying to load various settings from the JSON secrets file when using OAuth2 service account flow. Thrown if private_key key is missing in the JSON file.

data.name: QuotesNotClosedInCsvLine
data.value: Quotes not closed in csv record.
data.comment: Used for CsvException by CsvFile.SplitCsvLine if text parameter has an unclosed quote.

data.name: ServiceCannotBeNull
data.value: Service cannot be null
data.comment: Used by AuthTokenCache when an empty service is passed to it.

data.name: SignatureCannotBeNull
data.value: Cache signature cannot be null.
data.comment: Used for ArgumentException by InMemoryTokenCache class.

data.name: SourceStreamIsNotReadable
data.value: Source stream is not readable.
data.comment: Used for ArgumentException by MediaUtilities.CopyStream if source stream is not readable.

data.name: StartIndexShouldBeLessThanEndIndex
data.value: Start index should be less than end index.
data.comment: Used for ArgumentException by ExtractAndAddItem if startIndex > endIndex.

data.name: StringIndexOutOfBounds
data.value: This parameter should be greater than 0 and less than the length of text.
data.comment: Used for ArgumentOutOfRangeException wherever string index is out of bounds.

data.name: TargetStreamIsNotWritable
data.value: Target stream is not writable.
data.comment: Used for ArgumentException by MediaUtilities.CopyStream if target stream is not writable.

data.name: TextCannotBeNull
data.value: Text to split cannot be null.
data.comment: Used for ArgumentNullException by CsvFile.SplitCsvLine for 'text' parameter.

data.name: UnknownTraceSource
data.value: Unknown trace source : {0}.
data.comment: Used by TraceUtilites.GetSource method when someone requests an unknown trace source.

data.name: UnregisteredServiceTypeRequested
data.value: Unregistered service type {0} was requested.
data.comment: Used for InvalidCastException by AdsUser.GetService for serviceSignature parameter if an unregistered service type is requested.
